[I] A small vi/ex editor for editing UTF-8 text

[T] Neatvi is a small vi/ex editor for editing UTF-8 text. It supports syntax
[T] highlighting, multiple windows, right-to-left languages, and keymaps.

[U] https://dev.rudi.ir/

[A] Ali Gholami Rudi
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/editor
[F] CROSS

[L] OpenSource
[V] 19

[D] 4effe1b2231a0504b96b17b58c6d5eb715046c4c5ad270376d717a1d neatvi-19.tar.gz https://github.com/aligrudi/neatvi/archive/19/

makeinstopt=
hook_add postmake 5 'cp -vf vi $root$bindir/neatvi'
